snippet.title: Worship reveal trailer - PC Gaming Show 2024
snippet.description:
Grow your cult… with your friends': Worship's new trailer shows off how much chaos you can cause in this dark rogue like where you build a cutesy cult, summon monsters get up to all sorts of hijinks.
